messages.message:
Hi. Are the AI Hub file upload limitations (detailed in docs (https://aihub.instabase.com/docs/aihub/policies/limitations/index.html)) hard upper limits for this particular environment or more broadly for all deployments?
> Attaching here a 1182 page Selling Guide from Fannie Mae. This document / potential use case was raised by Chase Home Lending, where today it is reviewed during loan origination processes to ensure compliance and underwriting standards are met.
> Is the only option with AI Hub to split the document into sections and upload multiple smaller documents?

I believe there is a ticket tracking this @Tom Murphy.

@Will McDermott is this the same thing you're focused on with the TPR managers?
@Tom @Tom Murphy yes there’s a ticket tracking expanding file upload size (currently limited at 50MB). Will find it and link it here…
